    WHEN t."OperationSiteid" IS NOT NULL THEN o."Name"
    ELSE NULL

    ELSE NULL

    WHERE e."DepartmentId" = @__id_0

) AS t

) AS t

        INNER JOIN "Equipments" AS e0 ON e."EquipmentsId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE (m."Id" = e."MaintenancePlanId") AND (e0."Id" = @__Id_0))
    LIMIT @__p_1
) AS t

    LEFT JOIN "Models" AS m0 ON e."ModelId" = m0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "EquipmentType" AS e0 ON e."EquipmentTypeId" = e0."Id"
    WHERE e."Id" = @__id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "MaintenanceSettings" AS m1 ON t."Id" = m1."EquipmentId"
LEFT JOIN "UsageHistories" AS u ON t."Id" = u."EquipmentId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e1."EquipmentsId", e1."PartId", p."Id", p."Code", p."CreatedBy", p."CreatedDate", p."IsActive", p."IsDeleted", p."ModifiedBy", p."Name", p."RemovalDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "EquipmentPart" AS e1
    INNER JOIN "Parts" AS p ON e1."PartId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."EquipmentsId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e2."EquipmentsId", e2."MaintenancePlanId", m2."Id", m2."Code", m2."CreatedBy", m2."CreatedDate", m2."Description", m2."IsActive", m2."IsDeleted", m2."MPChecked", m2."MetricType", m2."MetricTypeName", m2."ModifiedBy", m2."Name", m2."RemovalDate", m2."Status", m2."UpdatedDate", m3."Id" AS "Id0", m3."CreatedBy" AS "CreatedBy0", m3."CreatedDate" AS "CreatedDate0", m3."DatePeriod", m3."EquipmentId", m3."IsActive" AS "IsActive0", m3."IsDeleted" AS "IsDeleted0", m3."IsMpCompleted", m3."MaintenancePlanId" AS "MaintenancePlanId0", m3."ModifiedBy" AS "ModifiedBy0", m3."MpName", m3."RemovalDate" AS "RemovalDate0", m3."ResetDate", m3."SequenceDateValue", m3."SequenceValue", m3."SsequencePeriod", m3."StartValue", m3."UpdatedDate" AS "UpdatedDate0", m3."UpdatedValue"
    FROM "EquipmentMaintenancePlan" AS e2
    INNER JOIN "MaintenancePlan" AS m2 ON e2."MaintenancePlanId" = m2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "MaintenanceSettings" AS m3 ON m2."Id" = m3."MaintenancePlanId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."EquipmentsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t."Id3", t."Id4", m1."Id", u."Id", t0."EquipmentsId", t0."PartId", t0."Id", t1."EquipmentsId", t1."MaintenancePlanId", t1."Id"

    INNER JOIN "Equipments" AS e2 ON e1."EquipmentsId" = e2."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."MaintenancePlanId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."EquipmentsId", t0."MaintenancePlanId"

    LEFT JOIN "EquipmentType" AS e0 ON e."EquipmentTypeId" = e0."Id"
    WHERE e."Id" = @__id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "MaintenanceSettings" AS m1 ON t."Id" = m1."EquipmentId"
LEFT JOIN "UsageHistories" AS u ON t."Id" = u."EquipmentId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e1."EquipmentsId", e1."PartId", p."Id", p."Code", p."CreatedBy", p."CreatedDate", p."IsActive", p."IsDeleted", p."ModifiedBy", p."Name", p."RemovalDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "EquipmentPart" AS e1
    INNER JOIN "Parts" AS p ON e1."PartId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."EquipmentsId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e2."EquipmentsId", e2."MaintenancePlanId", m2."Id", m2."Code", m2."CreatedBy", m2."CreatedDate", m2."Description", m2."IsActive", m2."IsDeleted", m2."MPChecked", m2."MetricType", m2."MetricTypeName", m2."ModifiedBy", m2."Name", m2."RemovalDate", m2."Status", m2."UpdatedDate", m3."Id" AS "Id0", m3."CreatedBy" AS "CreatedBy0", m3."CreatedDate" AS "CreatedDate0", m3."DatePeriod", m3."EquipmentId", m3."IsActive" AS "IsActive0", m3."IsDeleted" AS "IsDeleted0", m3."IsMpCompleted", m3."MaintenancePlanId" AS "MaintenancePlanId0", m3."ModifiedBy" AS "ModifiedBy0", m3."MpName", m3."RemovalDate" AS "RemovalDate0", m3."ResetDate", m3."SequenceDateValue", m3."SequenceValue", m3."SsequencePeriod", m3."StartValue", m3."UpdatedDate" AS "UpdatedDate0", m3."UpdatedValue"
    FROM "EquipmentMaintenancePlan" AS e2
    INNER JOIN "MaintenancePlan" AS m2 ON e2."MaintenancePlanId" = m2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "MaintenanceSettings" AS m3 ON m2."Id" = m3."MaintenancePlanId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."EquipmentsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t."Id3", t."Id4", m1."Id", u."Id", t0."EquipmentsId", t0."PartId", t0."Id", t1."EquipmentsId", t1."MaintenancePlanId", t1."Id"

        INNER JOIN "Equipments" AS e0 ON e."EquipmentsId" = e0."Id"

    LIMIT @__p_1
) AS t

o."Name" AS "Name2", o."RemovalDate" AS "RemovalDate2", o."UpdatedDate" AS "UpdatedDate2", m0."Id" AS "Id3", m0."Code" AS "Code1", m0."CreatedBy" AS "CreatedBy3", m0."CreatedDate" AS "CreatedDate3", m0."IsActive" AS "IsActive3", m0."IsDeleted" AS "IsDeleted3", m0."ModifiedBy" AS "ModifiedBy3", m0."Name" AS "Name3", m0."RemovalDate" AS "RemovalDate3", m0."RemovalReason" AS "RemovalReason0", m0."UpdatedDate" AS "UpdatedDate3", e0."Id" AS "Id4", e0."CreatedBy" AS "CreatedBy4", e0."CreatedDate" AS "CreatedDate4", e0."IsActive" AS "IsActive4", e0."IsDeleted" AS "IsDeleted4", e0."ModifiedBy" AS "ModifiedBy4", e0."Name" AS "Name4", e0."RemovalDate" AS "RemovalDate4", e0."UpdatedDate" AS "UpdatedDate4"
    FROM "Equipments" AS e
    LEFT JOIN "Departments" AS d ON e."DepartmentId" = d."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Manufactures" AS m ON e."ManufactureId" = m."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "OperationSites" AS o ON e."OperationSiteid" = o."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Models" AS m0 ON e."ModelId" = m0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "EquipmentType" AS e0 ON e."EquipmentTypeId" = e0."Id"
    WHERE e."Id" = @__id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "MaintenanceSettings" AS m1 ON t."Id" = m1."EquipmentId"
LEFT JOIN "UsageHistories" AS u ON t."Id" = u."EquipmentId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e1."EquipmentsId", e1."PartId", p."Id", p."Code", p."CreatedBy", p."CreatedDate", p."IsActive", p."IsDeleted", p."ModifiedBy", p."Name", p."RemovalDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "EquipmentPart" AS e1
    INNER JOIN "Parts" AS p ON e1."PartId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."EquipmentsId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e2."EquipmentsId", e2."MaintenancePlanId", m2."Id", m2."Code", m2."CreatedBy", m2."CreatedDate", m2."Description", m2."IsActive", m2."IsDeleted", m2."MPChecked", m2."MetricType", m2."MetricTypeName", m2."ModifiedBy", m2."Name", m2."RemovalDate", m2."Status", m2."UpdatedDate", m3."Id" AS "Id0", m3."CreatedBy" AS "CreatedBy0", m3."CreatedDate" AS "CreatedDate0", m3."DatePeriod", m3."EquipmentId", m3."IsActive" AS "IsActive0", m3."IsDeleted" AS "IsDeleted0", m3."IsMpCompleted", m3."MaintenancePlanId" AS "MaintenancePlanId0", m3."ModifiedBy" AS "ModifiedBy0", m3."MpName", m3."RemovalDate" AS "RemovalDate0", m3."ResetDate", m3."SequenceDateValue", m3."SequenceValue", m3."SsequencePeriod", m3."StartValue", m3."UpdatedDate" AS "UpdatedDate0", m3."UpdatedValue"
    FROM "EquipmentMaintenancePlan" AS e2
    INNER JOIN "MaintenancePlan" AS m2 ON e2."MaintenancePlanId" = m2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "MaintenanceSettings" AS m3 ON m2."Id" = m3."MaintenancePlanId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."EquipmentsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t."Id3", t."Id4", m1."Id", u."Id", t0."EquipmentsId", t0."PartId", t0."Id", t1."EquipmentsId", t1."MaintenancePlanId", t1."Id"

LEFT JOIN "Manufactures" AS m ON e."ManufactureId" = m."Id"

LEFT JOIN "Models" AS m0 ON e."ModelId" = m0."Id"

) AS t0 ON e."Id" = t0."EquipmentsId"

AS "ModifiedBy4", e0."Name" AS "Name4", e0."RemovalDate" AS "RemovalDate4", e0."UpdatedDate" AS "UpdatedDate4"
    FROM "Equipments" AS e
    LEFT JOIN "Departments" AS d ON e."DepartmentId" = d."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Manufactures" AS m ON e."ManufactureId" = m."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "OperationSites" AS o ON e."OperationSiteid" = o."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Models" AS m0 ON e."ModelId" = m0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "EquipmentType" AS e0 ON e."EquipmentTypeId" = e0."Id"
    WHERE e."Id" = @__id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "MaintenanceSettings" AS m1 ON t."Id" = m1."EquipmentId"
LEFT JOIN "UsageHistories" AS u ON t."Id" = u."EquipmentId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e1."EquipmentsId", e1."PartId", p."Id", p."Code", p."CreatedBy", p."CreatedDate", p."IsActive", p."IsDeleted", p."ModifiedBy", p."Name", p."RemovalDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "EquipmentPart" AS e1
    INNER JOIN "Parts" AS p ON e1."PartId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."EquipmentsId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e2."EquipmentsId", e2."MaintenancePlanId", m2."Id", m2."Code", m2."CreatedBy", m2."CreatedDate", m2."Description", m2."IsActive", m2."IsDeleted", m2."MPChecked", m2."MetricType", m2."MetricTypeName", m2."ModifiedBy", m2."Name", m2."RemovalDate", m2."Status", m2."UpdatedDate", m3."Id" AS "Id0", m3."CreatedBy" AS "CreatedBy0", m3."CreatedDate" AS "CreatedDate0", m3."DatePeriod", m3."EquipmentId", m3."IsActive" AS "IsActive0", m3."IsDeleted" AS "IsDeleted0", m3."IsMpCompleted", m3."MaintenancePlanId" AS "MaintenancePlanId0", m3."ModifiedBy" AS "ModifiedBy0", m3."MpName", m3."RemovalDate" AS "RemovalDate0", m3."ResetDate", m3."SequenceDateValue", m3."SequenceValue", m3."SsequencePeriod", m3."StartValue", m3."UpdatedDate" AS "UpdatedDate0", m3."UpdatedValue"
    FROM "EquipmentMaintenancePlan" AS e2
    INNER JOIN "MaintenancePlan" AS m2 ON e2."MaintenancePlanId" = m2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "MaintenanceSettings" AS m3 ON m2."Id" = m3."MaintenancePlanId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."EquipmentsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t."Id3", t."Id4", m1."Id", u."Id", t0."EquipmentsId", t0."PartId", t0."Id", t1."EquipmentsId", t1."MaintenancePlanId", t1."Id"

LEFT JOIN "Manufactures" AS m ON e."ManufactureId" = m."Id"
LEFT JOIN "OperationSites" AS o ON e."OperationSiteid" = o."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Models" AS m0 ON e."ModelId" = m0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "EquipmentType" AS e0 ON e."EquipmentTypeId" = e0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "MaintenanceSettings" AS m1 ON e."Id" = m1."EquipmentId"
LEFT JOIN "UsageHistories" AS u ON e."Id" = u."EquipmentId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e1."EquipmentsId", e1."PartId", p."Id", p."Code", p."CreatedBy", p."CreatedDate", p."IsActive", p."IsDeleted", p."ModifiedBy", p."Name", p."RemovalDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "EquipmentPart" AS e1
    INNER JOIN "Parts" AS p ON e1."PartId" = p."Id"
) AS t ON e."Id" = t."EquipmentsId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e2."EquipmentsId", e2."MaintenancePlanId", m2."Id", m2."Code", m2."CreatedBy", m2."CreatedDate", m2."Description", m2."IsActive", m2."IsDeleted", m2."MPChecked", m2."MetricType", m2."MetricTypeName", m2."ModifiedBy", m2."Name", m2."RemovalDate", m2."Status", m2."UpdatedDate", m3."Id" AS "Id0", m3."CreatedBy" AS "CreatedBy0", m3."CreatedDate" AS "CreatedDate0", m3."DatePeriod", m3."EquipmentId", m3."IsActive" AS "IsActive0", m3."IsDeleted" AS "IsDeleted0", m3."IsMpCompleted", m3."MaintenancePlanId" AS "MaintenancePlanId0", m3."ModifiedBy" AS "ModifiedBy0", m3."MpName", m3."RemovalDate" AS "RemovalDate0", m3."ResetDate", m3."SequenceDateValue", m3."SequenceValue", m3."SsequencePeriod", m3."StartValue", m3."UpdatedDate" AS "UpdatedDate0", m3."UpdatedValue"
    FROM "EquipmentMaintenancePlan" AS e2
    INNER JOIN "MaintenancePlan" AS m2 ON e2."MaintenancePlanId" = m2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "MaintenanceSettings" AS m3 ON m2."Id" = m3."MaintenancePlanId"
) AS t0 ON e."Id" = t0."EquipmentsId"
WHERE e."Id" = @__id_0
ORDER BY e."Id", d."Id", m."Id", o."Id", m0."Id", e0."Id", m1."Id", u."Id", t."EquipmentsId", t."PartId", t."Id", t0."EquipmentsId", t0."MaintenancePlanId", t0."Id"

    FROM "Equipments" AS e
    LEFT JOIN "Departments" AS d ON e."DepartmentId" = d."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Manufactures" AS m ON e."ManufactureId" = m."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "OperationSites" AS o ON e."OperationSiteid" = o."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Models" AS m0 ON e."ModelId" = m0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "EquipmentType" AS e0 ON e."EquipmentTypeId" = e0."Id"
    WHERE e."Id" = @__id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "MaintenanceSettings" AS m1 ON t."Id" = m1."EquipmentId"
LEFT JOIN "UsageHistories" AS u ON t."Id" = u."EquipmentId"

    SELECT e1."EquipmentsId", e1."PartId", p."Id", p."Code", p."CreatedBy", p."CreatedDate", p."IsActive", p."IsDeleted", p."ModifiedBy", p."Name", p."RemovalDate", p."UpdatedDate"

    LEFT JOIN "MaintenanceSettings" AS m3 ON m2."Id" = m3."MaintenancePlanId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."EquipmentsId"

SELECT t."Id", t."Status", t."Name", t."Description", t."LastMaintenaceDate" AS "LastMaintenace", t."CurrentValue", CASE
    WHEN t."OperationSiteid" IS NOT NULL THEN o."Name"
    ELSE NULL
END AS "OperationSite", CASE
    WHEN t."EquipmentTypeId" IS NOT NULL THEN e0."Name"
    ELSE NULL
END AS "Type", t."ProductionYear", t."SeriaNumber", t."MpCompleted" AS "MpTime"
FROM (
    SELECT e."Id", e."CurrentValue", e."DepartmentId", e."Description", e."EquipmentTypeId", e."IsActive", e."IsDeleted", e."LastMaintenaceDate", e."MpCompleted", e."Name", e."OperationSiteid", e."ProductionYear", e."SeriaNumber", e."Status"

    WHERE e."DepartmentId" = @__id_0

) AS t

    SELECT e1."EquipmentsId", e1."PartId", p."Id", p."Code", p."CreatedBy", p."CreatedDate", p."IsActive", p."IsDeleted", p."ModifiedBy", p."Name", p."RemovalDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "EquipmentPart" AS e1
    INNER JOIN "Parts" AS p ON e1."PartId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."EquipmentsId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e2."EquipmentsId", e2."MaintenancePlanId", m2."Id", m2."Code", m2."CreatedBy", m2."CreatedDate", m2."Description", m2."IsActive", m2."IsDeleted", m2."MPChecked", m2."MetricType", m2."MetricTypeName", m2."ModifiedBy", m2."Name", m2."RemovalDate", m2."Status", m2."UpdatedDate", m3."Id" AS "Id0", m3."CreatedBy" AS "CreatedBy0", m3."CreatedDate" AS "CreatedDate0", m3."DatePeriod", m3."EquipmentId", m3."IsActive" AS "IsActive0", m3."IsDeleted" AS "IsDeleted0", m3."IsMpCompleted", m3."MaintenancePlanId" AS "MaintenancePlanId0", m3."ModifiedBy" AS "ModifiedBy0", m3."MpName", m3."RemovalDate" AS "RemovalDate0", m3."ResetDate", m3."SequenceDateValue", m3."SequenceValue", m3."SsequencePeriod", m3."StartValue", m3."UpdatedDate" AS "UpdatedDate0", m3."UpdatedValue"
    FROM "EquipmentMaintenancePlan" AS e2
    INNER JOIN "MaintenancePlan" AS m2 ON e2."MaintenancePlanId" = m2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "MaintenanceSettings" AS m3 ON m2."Id" = m3."MaintenancePlanId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."EquipmentsId"

    SELECT e1."EquipmentsId", e1."MaintenancePlanId", e2."Id", e2."Capacity", e2."Color", e2."CreatedBy", e2."CreatedDate", e2."CurrentValue", e2."DepartmentId", e2."Description", e2."EquipmentTypeId", e2."Identification", e2."ImagUrl", e2."IsActive", e2."IsDeleted", e2."IsIdle", e2."IsNotified", e2."LastMaintenaceDate", e2."ManufactureId", e2."ModelId", e2."ModifiedBy", e2."MpCompleted", e2."Name", e2."OperationSiteid", e2."ProductionYear", e2."RemovalDate", e2."ResetValue", e2."SeriaNumber", e2."SquenceValue", e2."Status", e2."UnitNumber", e2."UpdatedDate", e2."usageLocation"
    FROM "EquipmentMaintenancePlan" AS e1
    INNER JOIN "Equipments" AS e2 ON e1."EquipmentsId" = e2."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."MaintenancePlanId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."EquipmentsId", t0."MaintenancePlanId"

) AS t

SELECT t."Id", t."Status", t."Name", t."Description", t."LastMaintenaceDate" AS "LastMaintenace", t."CurrentValue", CASE
    WHEN t."OperationSiteid" IS NOT NULL THEN o."Name"
    ELSE NULL
END AS "OperationSite", CASE
    WHEN t."EquipmentTypeId" IS NOT NULL THEN e0."Name"
    ELSE NULL
END AS "Type", t."ProductionYear", t."SeriaNumber", t."MpCompleted" AS "MpTime"

    SELECT e."Id", e."CurrentValue", e."DepartmentId", e."Description", e."EquipmentTypeId", e."IsActive", e."IsDeleted", e."LastMaintenaceDate", e."MpCompleted", e."Name", e."OperationSiteid", e."ProductionYear", e."SeriaNumber", e."Status"

    WHERE e."DepartmentId" = @__id_0
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "OperationSites" AS o ON t."OperationSiteid" = o."Id"
LEFT JOIN "EquipmentType" AS e0 ON t."EquipmentTypeId" = e0."Id"

SELECT o."Id", o."Name", o."Code", CASE
    WHEN o."DepartmentId" IS NOT NULL THEN d."Name"
    ELSE NULL
END AS "Department", o."DepartmentId", o."IsActive", o."IsDeleted", o."CreatedDate", o."CreatedBy", o."ModifiedBy", o."UpdatedDate", o."RemovalDate"
FROM "OperationSites" AS o
LEFT JOIN "Departments" AS d ON o."DepartmentId" = d."Id"

    SELECT e1."EquipmentsId", e1."PartId", p."Id", p."Code", p."CreatedBy", p."CreatedDate", p."IsActive", p."IsDeleted", p."ModifiedBy", p."Name", p."RemovalDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "EquipmentPart" AS e1
    INNER JOIN "Parts" AS p ON e1."PartId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."EquipmentsId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e2."EquipmentsId", e2."MaintenancePlanId", m2."Id", m2."Code", m2."CreatedBy", m2."CreatedDate", m2."Description", m2."IsActive", m2."IsDeleted", m2."MPChecked", m2."MetricType", m2."MetricTypeName", m2."ModifiedBy", m2."Name", m2."RemovalDate", m2."Status", m2."UpdatedDate", m3."Id" AS "Id0", m3."CreatedBy" AS "CreatedBy0", m3."CreatedDate" AS "CreatedDate0", m3."DatePeriod", m3."EquipmentId", m3."IsActive" AS "IsActive0", m3."IsDeleted" AS "IsDeleted0", m3."IsMpCompleted", m3."MaintenancePlanId" AS "MaintenancePlanId0", m3."ModifiedBy" AS "ModifiedBy0", m3."MpName", m3."RemovalDate" AS "RemovalDate0", m3."ResetDate", m3."SequenceDateValue", m3."SequenceValue", m3."SsequencePeriod", m3."StartValue", m3."UpdatedDate" AS "UpdatedDate0", m3."UpdatedValue"
    FROM "EquipmentMaintenancePlan" AS e2
    INNER JOIN "MaintenancePlan" AS m2 ON e2."MaintenancePlanId" = m2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "MaintenanceSettings" AS m3 ON m2."Id" = m3."MaintenancePlanId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."EquipmentsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t."Id3", t."Id4", m1."Id", u."Id", t0."EquipmentsId", t0."PartId", t0."Id", t1."EquipmentsId", t1."MaintenancePlanId", t1."Id"

    ELSE NULL

END AS "Type", t."ProductionYear", t."SeriaNumber", t."MpCompleted" AS "MpTime"
FROM (
    SELECT e."Id", e."CurrentValue", e."DepartmentId", e."Description", e."EquipmentTypeId", e."IsActive", e."IsDeleted", e."LastMaintenaceDate", e."MpCompleted", e."Name", e."OperationSiteid", e."ProductionYear", e."SeriaNumber", e."Status"

    WHERE e."DepartmentId" = @__id_0
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "OperationSites" AS o ON t."OperationSiteid" = o."Id"
LEFT JOIN "EquipmentType" AS e0 ON t."EquipmentTypeId" = e0."Id"
WHERE ((t."IsDeleted" = FALSE) AND (t."IsActive" = TRUE)) AND (t."DepartmentId" = @__id_0)

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."CreatedBy", t."CreatedDate", t."Description", t."IsActive", t."IsDeleted", t."MPChecked", t."MetricType", t."MetricTypeName", t."ModifiedBy", t."Name", t."RemovalDate", t."Status", t."UpdatedDate", t0."EquipmentsId", t0."MaintenancePlanId", t0."Id", t0."Capacity", t0."Color", t0."CreatedBy", t0."CreatedDate", t0."CurrentValue", t0."DepartmentId", t0."Description", t0."EquipmentTypeId", t0."Identification", t0."ImagUrl", t0."IsActive", t0."IsDeleted", t0."IsIdle", t0."IsNotified", t0."LastMaintenaceDate", t0."ManufactureId", t0."ModelId", t0."ModifiedBy", t0."MpCompleted", t0."Name", t0."OperationSiteid", t0."ProductionYear", t0."RemovalDate", t0."ResetValue", t0."SeriaNumber", t0."SquenceValue", t0."Status", t0."UnitNumber", t0."UpdatedDate", t0."usageLocation"
FROM (
    SELECT m."Id", m."Code", m."CreatedBy", m."CreatedDate", m."Description", m."IsActive", m."IsDeleted", m."MPChecked", m."MetricType", m."MetricTypeName", m."ModifiedBy", m."Name", m."RemovalDate", m."Status", m."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "MaintenancePlan" AS m
    WHERE EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EquipmentMaintenancePlan" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Equipments" AS e0 ON e."EquipmentsId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE (m."Id" = e."MaintenancePlanId") AND (e0."Id" = @__Id_0))
    LIMIT @__p_1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e1."EquipmentsId", e1."MaintenancePlanId", e2."Id", e2."Capacity", e2."Color", e2."CreatedBy", e2."CreatedDate", e2."CurrentValue", e2."DepartmentId", e2."Description", e2."EquipmentTypeId", e2."Identification", e2."ImagUrl", e2."IsActive", e2."IsDeleted", e2."IsIdle", e2."IsNotified", e2."LastMaintenaceDate", e2."ManufactureId", e2."ModelId", e2."ModifiedBy", e2."MpCompleted", e2."Name", e2."OperationSiteid", e2."ProductionYear", e2."RemovalDate", e2."ResetValue", e2."SeriaNumber", e2."SquenceValue", e2."Status", e2."UnitNumber", e2."UpdatedDate", e2."usageLocation"
    FROM "EquipmentMaintenancePlan" AS e1
    INNER JOIN "Equipments" AS e2 ON e1."EquipmentsId" = e2."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."MaintenancePlanId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."EquipmentsId", t0."MaintenancePlanId"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."CreatedBy", t."CreatedDate", t."Description", t."IsActive", t."IsDeleted", t."MPChecked", t."MetricType", t."MetricTypeName", t."ModifiedBy", t."Name", t."RemovalDate", t."Status", t."UpdatedDate", t0."EquipmentsId", t0."MaintenancePlanId", t0."Id", t0."Capacity", t0."Color", t0."CreatedBy", t0."CreatedDate", t0."CurrentValue", t0."DepartmentId", t0."Description", t0."EquipmentTypeId", t0."Identification", t0."ImagUrl", t0."IsActive", t0."IsDeleted", t0."IsIdle", t0."IsNotified", t0."LastMaintenaceDate", t0."ManufactureId", t0."ModelId", t0."ModifiedBy", t0."MpCompleted", t0."Name", t0."OperationSiteid", t0."ProductionYear", t0."RemovalDate", t0."ResetValue", t0."SeriaNumber", t0."SquenceValue", t0."Status", t0."UnitNumber", t0."UpdatedDate", t0."usageLocation"
FROM (
    SELECT m."Id", m."Code", m."CreatedBy", m."CreatedDate", m."Description", m."IsActive", m."IsDeleted", m."MPChecked", m."MetricType", m."MetricTypeName", m."ModifiedBy", m."Name", m."RemovalDate", m."Status", m."UpdatedDate"

    WHERE EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EquipmentMaintenancePlan" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Equipments" AS e0 ON e."EquipmentsId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE (m."Id" = e."MaintenancePlanId") AND (e0."Id" = @__Id_0))
    LIMIT @__p_1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e1."EquipmentsId", e1."MaintenancePlanId", e2."Id", e2."Capacity", e2."Color", e2."CreatedBy", e2."CreatedDate", e2."CurrentValue", e2."DepartmentId", e2."Description", e2."EquipmentTypeId", e2."Identification", e2."ImagUrl", e2."IsActive", e2."IsDeleted", e2."IsIdle", e2."IsNotified", e2."LastMaintenaceDate", e2."ManufactureId", e2."ModelId", e2."ModifiedBy", e2."MpCompleted", e2."Name", e2."OperationSiteid", e2."ProductionYear", e2."RemovalDate", e2."ResetValue", e2."SeriaNumber", e2."SquenceValue", e2."Status", e2."UnitNumber", e2."UpdatedDate", e2."usageLocation"
    FROM "EquipmentMaintenancePlan" AS e1
    INNER JOIN "Equipments" AS e2 ON e1."EquipmentsId" = e2."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."MaintenancePlanId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."EquipmentsId", t0."MaintenancePlanId"
